                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17701024-31-off145 t17701024-31-cd146"></join>, about the hour of one in the night, and stealing two cotton gowns, one linen and cotton counter pane, three aprons, a linen sleeve, a cotton skirt, a cotton nightgown, two linen table-cloths, a linen and worsted chair bottom, and eight linen cloth, the property of the said 
                     <persName id="t17701024-31-person247">
